title: Albert Lee & Hogan's Heroes Live In Paris
description:
On December 1st, 2003, Albert Lee & Hogan's Heroes appeared before an ecstatic crowd at the legendary New Morning in Paris. Fortunately, cameras were there to record the event, and Live In Paris is a full record of that magical evening. Here you'll find the complete show, as played on the night by Albert and the guys, and featuring some of the most dazzling guitar work you'll ever hear or see. So if you're ready for a two-hour-long feast of rip-roaring rock 'n' roll and cutting-edge country music, as served up by the acknowledged master of the art and his great band, dig in and bon appetit!

Screen Ratio: Widescreen (16:9)
Audio Track:  Dolby Digital 5.1
Running Time: 102 mins
